Class CostCenterContainerService

java.lang.Object
  atg.nucleus.GenericService
      atg.b2bcommerce.order.purchase.CostCenterContainerService
All Implemented Interfaces:
AdminableService, ApplicationLogging, CommerceIdentifierCostCenterContainer, ComponentNameResolver, atg.b2bcommerce.order.CostCenterConstants, CostCenterMapContainer, java.util.EventListener, NameContextBindingListener, NameContextElement, NameResolver, java.io.Serializable, Service, ServiceListener
public class CostCenterContainerService
extends GenericService
implements CostCenterMapContainer, CommerceIdentifierCostCenterContainer, atg.b2bcommerce.order.CostCenterConstants

The CostCenterContainerService is a convenient session scoped component which implements both the CostCenterMapContainer and the CommerceIdentifierCostCenterContainer interfaces. This service is responsible for keeping track of both the user's authorized CostCenters, as well as the CommerceIdentifierCostCenter objects for a user's Order.
